latestIgtvVideos.title: #PRP Therapy for #hairfall
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hola girls! So I know a lot of us out there suffer from immense hairfall. There could be a zillion reasons for it  including, postpartum stress, anxiety, hormonal imbalance, etc. 

I have myself tried everything under the sun but nothing seemed to be showing visible results. 

But the good news is, I may have found a solution for you all. 
 
Your one stop place for all your haircare and skin needs @drzarasays . So I got the the above procedure done for myself which requires infusing your platelets with growth factorswhich have been derived from your blood,  and injecting it into your scalp. Though it may sound scary, it was an extremely safe procedure. This procedure is done at a 21 day interval .

After 4 sessions, I can confidently say that I have noticed an almost 80 percent reduction in my hairfall. My hair feels healthier and I just cannot recommend @drzarasays zara enough. 
 
So guys please do visit her with your hair or skin story and I assure you, you won’t be disappointed. This is my self pamper story, what’s yours ?

latestIgtvVideos.title: Enchanted Fantasy
Mastaani Look
Beauty talks with BSS
Maldives
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
MAJOR THROWBACK
 This trip to Maldives was just before i got to know i am pregnant...
This was the last trip I had been to and havent been anywhere since then !!!
I miss travelling terribly!
It gets really difficult to travel with my TWINNIES 💕
And I havent got time to plan any getaway since then although its been much needed.
This quarantine dreaming of the beaches and the serene veiw from this gorgeous water bungalow 😍 
Eagerly waiting for the next time I can pack my bags and travel to my next dream destination.
With all thats happening right now in the world really happy to be with my family and grateful that we are all in the pink of our health.Praying for the world to heal🙏🏻
Hoping for this pandemic to take reverse course at a mighty speed 😇
@alipetiwala 
@centararasfushiresortmaldives

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY Quarantine Haircut
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So it took aloottttttt of convincing to get @alipetiwala on my page as guest 😋 and more convincing to even allowing me to give him a haircut with no experience of it in the past 😂 
Had seen a DIY haircut tutorial on @tees_hairtales page so i thought of getting super ambitious and tried convincing @alipetiwala to volunteer 🙈

You can see how grumpy he was cuz he was FORCED to do this ! 😋 
But took God’s name and started with the trimming.

The haircut turned out okay..
Not at par with the professional hairstylist ... But I guess did the job for the time being... Please double tap to show some love for this crazy stupid video 😋 
Nice comments only please ! 😬
